wminc-desc: MaKim bɛɛ kpansim wiki nindaa gɔs n tis wikimedia Incubator
wminc-prefinfo-language: Fʋ pian'ʋk kanɛ ka fʋ mɔri tʋm la anɛ linɛ zi'e li mɛŋ yit wiki makirin la
wminc-prefinfo-code: Pian'ad la ISO 639 koot la ka fʋ mɔri tʋm kpɛ
wminc-prefinfo-project: Gaŋim Wikimedia la tʋʋm kanɛ ka fʋ tʋmmɛ li kpɛ
wminc-prefinfo-error: Fʋ gaŋ tʋʋma kanɛ bɔɔd pian'ad koot
wminc-error-move-unprefixed: Gbɛlʋŋ : lakir kanɛ ka fʋ mɔɔd ye fʋ vudig keŋ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|la pʋ mɔr a-sʋŋ-maal lakir sɔbʋgɔ bɛɛ li mɔri a-sʋŋ-maal sɔb gbɛlʋŋ ]].
wminc-error-unprefixed: Gbɛlʋŋ Lakir kaŋa pʋ mɔr a-sʋŋ-maa sɔbʋgɔ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|a-sʋŋ-maal sɔbʋg kae]].
wminc-error-unprefixed-suggest: Gbɛlʋŋ Lakir kaŋa pʋ mɔr a-sʋŋ-maal lakir laa. [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|unprefixed ]]! Fʋ tʋn'e maal lakir bɛ [[:$1]].
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Wiki kaŋa pʋn dɛŋim bɛ. Fʋ tʋn'e nyɛ lakir kaŋa bɛ $1 ni. Wiki la ya'a pa'a maalnɛ nannana, Bɛllimnɛ gu'usim aawa bɛɛ dabisa bi'ela hali ti paae saŋa kanɛ ka nimua bʋnam wʋsa kpɛn' na
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Lakir kaŋa anɛ tʋʋm yinne linɛ pʋ bɛ bɛɛ zaŋi niŋ kpɛ bʋn. Bɛllimnɛ kem $1 ni n ie wiki la.
randombytest-nopages: Lakisa kae fʋ wiki makir linɛ bɛ yʋ'ʋr paalʋ la nii :$1.
wminc-viewuserlang: Gɔsim tʋmtʋm pian'ad ka mak wiki
wminc-ip: "$1" anɛ IP adɛrɛs bɛɛ linɛ kʋ yuugɛ
action-viewuserlang: Gɔsim tʋmtʋm pian'ad ka mak wiki
right-viewuserlang: Gɔsim tʋmtʋm pian'ad ka mak wiki
wminc-listusers-testwiki: Fʋ gɔsidi tʋmtʋmnib banɛ maaligim zi'eli ba wiki makir bɛɛ kpansʋg la keŋ $1.
wminc-search-nocreate-nopref: Fʋ ie nɛ "$1". Bɛllimnɛ Maalim fʋ [[Special:Preferences|test wiki preference]] ala ka ti na yɛlif lakir kanɛ ka na nyaŋi maalɛ
wminc-search-nocreate-suggest: Fʋ ie nɛ "$1". Fʋ tʋn'e maal lakir bɛ fʋ wiki ni [[$3]]!
wminc-searchwiki-noresults: Si'el kae. Fʋ tʋn'e ie nɛ pian'ad koot,nɛ buudi yʋda nɛ yʋda banɛ bɛ fʋn mɔr pian'ad si'a sɔbir la ni bɛɛ na'asaal.
wminc-searchwiki-multiplematches: Fʋ ieeb la tuunl bɛɛ dɔlnɛ pian'ad banɛ dɔl la nwa':
wminc-searchwiki-match-englishname: "$1" la anɛ yʋ'ʋr tis $2 bɛ na'asaal pʋʋgin.
wminc-searchwiki-match-nativename: "$1" la anɛ yʋ'ʋr tis $2 bɛ pian'ad kan ni.
wminc-fs-settings-title: Maalimɛ fʋ wiki bɔɔdim an si'em.
wminc-fs-intro: Bu'odif ken-ken bɛ yiiga suozi'ela banɛ na sʋŋif nɛ baŋir ka fʋ tʋm. Sʋŋir na bɛɛ tisif fʋn na dɔl suosieba ka pin'il wiki paal.
wminc-fs-signup-text: Fʋ ya'a pʋn dɛŋim mɔr akaʋnt, bɛllimnɛ [$1 yɔ'ɔgim kpɛn']. Fʋ ya'a nam pʋ mɔr ayinnɛɛ,bɛllimnɛ [$2 maalim tʋʋma akaʋnt]. Li pʋ bɔɔda, amaa anɛ sa'alʋg bɛdegʋ ka li nɔkidi sɛkɛns bi'ela naamid
wminc-fs-settings-text:
Nannana kem [[Special:Preferences#mw-htmlform-i18n|your preferences]] ka tiaki fʋ wiki makir bɔɔdim zi'elʋg.
Yiiga bʋn anɛ pian'ad kanɛ ka fʋ mɔr tʋm la,ka gaŋi di bɛ yiiga suodɔlʋsʋg ni la,amaa la'am nɛ wala fʋ tʋn'e nyaŋi tiaki li.
Ka linɛ paas ayi' anɛ tʋʋm kanɛ ka fʋ bɔɔd ye sʋŋ paas la, ka linɛ paas atan' la anɛ tʋʋma la pian'ad koot kanɛ ka fʋ bɔɔd ye fʋ sʋŋ paas la.
Fʋ ya'a zi' koot laa, bɛllimnɛ bu'osimɛ ti[[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|manual]] bɛɛ bu'osim linɛ nwa' yɛla [[{{MediaWiki:Portal-url}}|help]].
wminc-fs-userpage-text: Nannana Bɛllimnɛ Maalim tʋʋma lakir $1 nɛ fʋ mɛŋ labaar yɛla bi'ela. Fʋ mɛ tʋn'e nyɛ link keŋɛ li ni n bɛ lakir kaŋa agɔl la ni.
wminc-fs-startwiki-text: Fʋ wiki prefix la anɛ $1. Fʋ tʋn'e pin'il wiki la n maan wiki la zug lakir bɛ $2 ni.
wminc-fs-startwiki-exists-text: Fʋ wiki prefix la anɛ $1. Zug lakir la bɛnɛ $2. Nannana fʋ tʋn'e la'as nɛ pian'ad kaŋa tʋmtʋmnib ka ya mɛ bɛɛ nɔbig nɔɔr yinne zak! Fʋ ya'a bɔɔd ye fʋ maal lakir, kʋdʋm sɔm yʋ'ʋr la kpɛn'ɛs ieeb daka kanɛ bɛɛ agɔl nwa, ka dɔl link kanɛ ka fʋ nyɛ la.
wminc-infopage-welcome: Bu'odif ken-ken bɛ Wikimedia Incubator tʋʋm kanɛ an Wikimedia ɛɛnbir la [[{{MediaWiki:Aboutpage}}|About]]
wminc-infopage-missingwiki-text: $1 yinne kanɛ bɛ pian'ad kaŋa ni nam pʋ bɛɛ
wminc-infopage-option-startwiki: Fʋ ya'a bɔɔd ye fʋ pin'il wiki kaŋa, bɛllimnɛ dɔl '''[$3 these steps ]''' nwa nɛ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|ti nu'ug tʋʋm]].
wminc-infopage-option-startsister: Fʋ ya'a bɔɔd ye pin'il wiki kaŋa, fʋ tʋn'e keŋ [$2 $1] ni.
wminc-infopage-option-languages-existing: Fʋ tʋn'e ie [//www.$1.org existing language edition of $1]
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-exi: Fʋ tʋn'e ie tʋʋma banɛ bɛ pian'ad kaŋa ni:
wminc-infopage-option-sisterprojects-oth: Fʋ tʋn'e ie tʋʋm sieb bɛ pian'ad kaŋa ni:
wminc-infopage-option-multilingual: Bɛdegʋ pʋʋgin ni, fʋ tʋn'e keŋ wiki kanɛ mɔr pian'ad bɛdegʋ:
wminc-infopage-createmainpage: Sɔm pian'ʋk kanɛ an ye "Zug Lakir" la kpɛn'ɛs pian'ad kaŋa ni:
wminc-infopage-contribute: Fʋ ya'a mi' pian'ad kaŋa, kpɛmisʋg bɛ tisif ye fʋ sʋŋ paas!
wminc-infopage-status-open: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki paalʋ kanɛ an Wikimedia Incubator.
wminc-infopage-status-imported: Incubator wiki kaŋa daa yinɛ $1 kpɛn' na lin da yɔ la nya'aŋ.
wminc-infopage-status-approved: [[meta:Special:MyLanguage/Language_committee|language committee]] siak di'e Incubator wiki kaŋa ka li kʋ yuugɛ ka na maal.
wminc-infopage-status-created: Buudi pian'ad Kpɛɛmnam yʋ'ʋn siak di'e tʋʋm kaŋa ka li yʋ'ʋn bɛ $1 nannana
wminc-infopage-status-beforeincubator: Tʋʋm kaŋa daa naam nɛ ka Wikimedia Incubator naan pin'il ka bɛ $1
wminc-infopage-error: Gbɛlʋŋ: {{#infopage}} tʋn'e nyaŋi nɔk tʋm nɛ prefixed lakisa ni ma'aa.
